3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | fanta | milk | hot-chocolate | sprite |

